Title name:
Business Process Reengineering Suggestion Agent

Problem Statement: 
Organizations struggle to identify inefficiencies in existing business processes and find actionable, improvements quickly. 

Data Requirements: Process documentation, performance data, workflow diagrams.

Expected Output: Detailed process improvement reports with suggested changes (based an pre-defined industry. enterprise standards, benchmarks etc beyond LLM) and expected benefits. Be creative to go beyond as you solve the above needs.



Planned enhancements:
    - Automated workflow simulation & visualization
    - KPI dashboard with before/after scenarios
    - Multi-agent optimization (cost/time/quality agents)
    - Voice-based interaction & mobile support
    - Persistent storage & enterprise connector (ERP/MES)
